WEBVTT

00:02:29.000 --> 00:02:32.240
Qolaversa, bu yomon husnixat,
lekin ba’zi muhim so’zlarni belgilab

00:02:33.600 --> 00:02:34.816
qo’ydim.
Tushunib oldiz.

00:02:34.840 --> 00:02:36.616
(Kulgu)

00:02:36.640 --> 00:02:37.840
Shunday qilib ...

00:02:39.280 --> 00:02:41.296
bu boshqa bir ko'rinishim edi.

00:02:41.320 --> 00:02:43.000
dunyoni zabt etuvchi.

00:02:43.880 --> 00:02:45.336
Xo’sh, ikki yildan so’ng

00:02:45.360 --> 00:02:49.296
menga Amerikaga borish 
imkoniyati taqdim etildi.

00:02:49.320 --> 00:02:50.896
Darhol rozi bo’ldim,

00:02:50.920 --> 00:02:53.136
chunki u yerda Bill Geyts yashaydi,
to’g’rimi?

00:02:53.160 --> 00:02:54.376
(Kulgu)

00:02:54.400 --> 00:02:57.040
Bu biznesdagi ilk sayohatim, deb o’yladim.

00:02:57.680 --> 00:02:59.856
So’ng, keyingi shiddatli 14 yil.

00:02:59.880 --> 00:03:01.296
30 yoshda edim.